  "3253830": {
    "name": "坦克竞技场：全面行动",
    "steam_appid": 3253830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/86df71dd73b523d4b94d012dac02c41b.avif?t=1745503537\" width=620 height=92 /></span><br><br>《坦克竞技场：全面行动》是一款以竞技为主题的大型多人军事类游戏，指挥超过400款不同的坦克、战车、直升机等军事武器，在2000x2000的宏大战场中与来自全球的其他玩家进行12v12的团队竞技比赛。穿梭于充满历史感的战场，体验坦克对抗与团队策略的激烈碰撞。酣畅淋漓的pvp战斗、策略至上的团队协作都将为您的游戏体验增加不一样的乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/18844100eeb7205981643c14e5cff91e.poster.avif?t=1745503537\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/18844100eeb7205981643c14e5cff91e.webm?t=1745503537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/18844100eeb7205981643c14e5cff91e.mp4?t=1745503537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >###坦克养成：打造属于你的战争机器</h2></strong><br>在《坦克竞技场：全面行动》中，坦克不仅是你的武器，更是你在战场上的伙伴。游戏内提供了多种国家的历史名坦，如德国的“虎王”、苏联的“T-34”、美国的“M4谢尔曼”等。每一辆坦克都有其独特的性能和战斗风格，你可以通过升级系统逐步提升坦克的装甲、防护、火力和机动性，打造出一辆符合自己战术需求的钢铁巨兽。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/a2f0cfbdfbec6e256217d7586aa7da6a.poster.avif?t=1745503537\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/a2f0cfbdfbec6e256217d7586aa7da6a.webm?t=1745503537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/a2f0cfbdfbec6e256217d7586aa7da6a.mp4?t=1745503537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >###天梯排位：挑战全球精英指挥官 </h2></strong><br>对于那些渴望证明自己实力的玩家，天梯排位系统将是你不容错过的挑战。排位赛会根据你的表现为你匹配全球范围内的对手，让你与世界各地的精英指挥官展开正面较量。通过在比赛中的出色表现，你将逐步提升自己的排名，并解锁专属奖励。排位赛不仅考验你的个人操作，还需要你对战场形势的敏锐判断以及团队配合的默契程度。每一场胜利都将为你的荣誉殿堂添上光辉的一笔，而失败则会成为你磨练战术的宝贵经验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/6a4b72204bc76ca199f2a8d53e86fd2d.poster.avif?t=1745503537\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/6a4b72204bc76ca199f2a8d53e86fd2d.webm?t=1745503537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/6a4b72204bc76ca199f2a8d53e86fd2d.mp4?t=1745503537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >###自定义外观：彰显你的个性与荣耀 </h2></strong><br>《坦克竞技场：全面行动》深知每位指挥官都希望在战场上拥有独特的标识。游戏内提供了丰富的自定义选项，你可以为自己的坦克选择各种涂装、贴花以及配件，甚至可以定制独一无二的旗帜。在战场上，你的坦克不仅是战争机器，更是你个人风格与荣耀的象征。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/ba948bf6ce91e4320faea9310e82dd06.poster.avif?t=1745503537\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/ba948bf6ce91e4320faea9310e82dd06.webm?t=1745503537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/ba948bf6ce91e4320faea9310e82dd06.mp4?t=1745503537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >### 组队策略：团队协作是制胜关键 </h2></strong><br>在《坦克竞技场：全面行动》中，个人英雄主义固然重要，但真正的胜利往往属于那些懂得团队协作的指挥官。游戏内设有多种多人对战模式，从5v5的小规模战斗到12v12的大型团队战，无论是正面突袭、侧翼包抄还是迂回打击，每一项战术的成功执行都依赖于队友之间的默契与配合。在战斗中，你需要时刻关注队友的动向，及时调整自己的策略，帮助团队取得最终的胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/6f45311bbeb0ee6518a1026bc5df64be.poster.avif?t=1745503537\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/6f45311bbeb0ee6518a1026bc5df64be.webm?t=1745503537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/6f45311bbeb0ee6518a1026bc5df64be.mp4?t=1745503537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >### 真实战场：感受二战的宏大战争氛围</h2> </strong><br>《坦克竞技场：全面行动》以其精美的画面和高度还原的战场场景，带你穿越回二战的硝烟之中。每一张地图都基于真实的二战战场设计，从东线的寒冷雪原到西线的巷战废墟，每一处细节都充满了历史感和代入感。结合逼真的音效和环境互动，你将在这里感受到最真实的战争氛围。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/9406a363544414ff6bbb6677a0db346e.poster.avif?t=1745503537\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/9406a363544414ff6bbb6677a0db346e.webm?t=1745503537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253830/extras/9406a363544414ff6bbb6677a0db346e.mp4?t=1745503537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
